content: Hi! I need to upload values from graph. Is there some resource type for that. I need Volume(L) to x-axis and Flow(L/s) to y-axis. There should be some time stamp to sort out the value pairs. Our software gives values every 10ms so there is going to be lot of values. Because of that it's necessary to get these values to one observation/resource.
Maybe check out Sampled Data (http://hl7.org/fhir/STU3/datatypes.html#SampledData) which you can throw into an Observation.
